Her optics caught the sight of Windlord & another. She was careful though, 
knowing that they had to have the perimeter defenses on. 

But.. she still continued on... she had to get there. Seemed that Windlord 
will be out of the way for a while. She wondered how the Maximals were doing. 
She glanced about as she walked up toward the other 2 newcomers, in her tiger 
mode. 

"Well... seems that we have some fresh.. "looking at the human. "Blood, "she 
stated in distaste then looking at the bot, "& oil."
